body:
Bumps [NJsonSchema](https://github.com/RicoSuter/NJsonSchema) from 10.1.8 to 10.1.11.
Release notes

Sourced from NJsonSchema's releases.

NJsonSchema v9.12.0 (Build-1852)

  • Bug fixes

NSwag v9.11.0 (Build 1849)

Possible breaking changes:

  • Inline dictionary or array inheritance (#785)
  • Improve allOf inheritance support (#783)

NSwag v9.10.75 (Build 1848)

DO NOT USE THIS RELEASE!

NSwag v9.10.74 (Build 1847)

Changes:

  • Improve range attribute handling, closes #775
  • Add exception docs, closes #776
  • Fix XmlDocumentationExtensions deadlock (#780)
  • Use allOf for all schemas in inheritance (#733)

NSwag v9.10.73 (Build 1846)

No release notes provided.
